Company profile:
Established in 2003, Resource Access Management Solutions Pvt. Ltd. (in short RAMSOL PVT LTD.), is a recruitment solutions organization that assist organizations employ people across the industry to accelerate candidate selection process. RAMSOL helps clients speed up recruitment through a unique combination of providing well screened profiles and services which ensures organizations complete selection process on time. Some of the leading IT and Non IT organizations are part of RAMSOL esteemed customer profile. Committed to innovation, RAMSOL works with a committed team of recruiters, to help our clients recruit personnel ahead of the competition and stay focused on their productivity.
